<plot>"Badass, Documentary" is filmmaker John Kelly's personal saga of hot rods and hubris. To create his persona, he infiltrates a gang of tough guys with fast cars. Ticket stubs, film clips, and old photographs recount his journey from restless suburban adolescent to aspiring hot rod junkie. When he finds himself alone on the wrong side of town, his motivation is called into question.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?056135</url></doc>
